page.title: 08FAMILY LIFE
page.content: On Wednesday I wake up at 7.45am.I get dressed and go downstairs to have breakfast.I take the dog for a walk, get my school things ready and go to school at 8.45am. by car with my mum. After I finish school mum and I go to pick my sister up from her school. When we get home I take our dog a walk and mum makes our tea.After tea I go jogging with my dad to keep us fit and then I watch television for a bit. At half past nine I go to bed.In bed I read any book I can find until about ten past ten then I go to sleep.
